#forum
######

Vanilla races share their sense of style, within reason.
This mod splits the vanilla races into two groups with each group sharing their clothing options within itself on the character creation screen. Not planning on adding the same group as recipes to the spinning wheel unless that gets requested.
Now properly extends these changes to generated villagers.

group 1: human apex hylotl glitch nova
group 2: avian floran

[URL='http://community.playstarbound.com/threads/124193/']MEGATHREAD[/URL]

PERMISSIONS: granted per license, gplv3, included in download.

